      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting. So you're saying the horror comes from that \"otherness.\" Can you give me an example of what those \"strange customs\" or \"rituals\" might actually look like in a neighborhood like that to make the reader feel like something is fundamentally wrong or unnatural about them?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
